title: Migrating Applications to IPv6.epub
description: If IPv6 is to be adopted on a large scale, the applications running on desktop systems, laptops, and even mobile devices need to work as well with this protocol as they do with IPv4. This concise book helps you explore the issues you need to address if you are to successfully migrate your apps to IPv6. Its ideal for application developers, system/network architects, product managers, and others involved in moving your network to IPv6.
